This paper is likely to belong to the Computer Vision (cs.CV) category as it deals with video salient object detection, which is a subfield of computer vision. The use of deep learning-based methods also suggests that it could be categorized under Machine Learning (cs.LG) and Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI). Additionally, the paper involves the use of optical flow, which is a common technique in Multimedia (cs.MM) research. Finally, the use of pseudo-labels suggests that it could also be categorized under Neural and Evolutionary Computing (cs.NE).
